    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CONFIGURABLE
      Level is configurable by the SARL user into the compiler configuration.
      DELEGATE
      Level is delegated to another issue (usually inside the Eclipse Java Compiler) in order to determine the issue level.
      ERROR
      It is an error.
      IGNORE
      Issue is ignored.
      INFO
      It is an information message.
      WARNING
      It is a warning.
